talogservice\", \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB数据库\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PD服务器超时错误：Error 9001 (HY000): PD server timeout: start timestamp may fall behind safe point，出现次数超过2300次\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常平均耗时9-11秒，异常时延长到11-13.5秒，延迟增加约20-25%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"下单操作失败：failed to prepare order: failed to get product，由于productcatalogservice无法正常获取商品信息\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现：\n\n1. **根因分析**：TiDB数据库的PD（Placement Driver）服务器出现超时，这是最下游的数据库服务问题。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**：\n   - TiDB → productcatalogservice → frontend/checkoutservice\n   - 所有调用productcatalogservice的服务都受到影响\n\n3. **具体影响**：\n   - **商品目录服务**：响应时间从9-11秒增加到11-13.5秒\n   - **购物车服务**：Redis操作延迟显著增加（HMSET从1.6秒增加到37秒）\n   - **下单服务**：因无法获取商品信息导致下单失败\n\n4. **网络vs服务**：延迟主要在服务处理层面，而非网络层面，因为数据库查询超时是主要问题。\n\n**建议**：检查TiDB集群的PD组件状态和性能，特别是检查是否存在存储瓶颈或网络分区问题。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "c1e38e2e-399", "component": "tidb-pd", "reason": "PD server timeout Error 9001 (HY000) causing start timestamp may fall behind safe point", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LogSearch(tidb-pd)", "observation": "Found Error 9001 (HY000): PD server timeout: start timestamp may fall behind safe point"}, {"step": 2, "action": "TraceAnalysis(c1e38e2e-399)", "observation": "productcatalogservice